## Task 5 — Fix Latvian diacritics in slug generation (B8)

`lib/slug.ts` generates slugs but does not transliterate Latvian characters, causing malformed URLs.

- Add a transliteration step at the top of the slug generation function, before any other processing.
- Map all Latvian diacritics to their Latin equivalents:

```
ā → a    Ā → A
č → c    Č → C
ē → e    Ē → E
ģ → g    Ģ → G
ī → i    Ī → I
ķ → k    Ķ → K
ļ → l    Ļ → L
ņ → n    Ņ → N
š → s    Š → S
ū → u    Ū → U
ž → z    Ž → Z
```

- Verify the function is used consistently for group slugs, event slugs, and any other entity slug generation.
- Test with a Latvian string (e.g. `"Rīgas Šaha Klubs"` → `"rigas-saha-klubs"`).

